    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075760/extras/049409148f820762807db846f0dc4468.poster.avif?t=1729871824\" width=800 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075760/extras/049409148f820762807db846f0dc4468.webm?t=1729871824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075760/extras/049409148f820762807db846f0dc4468.mp4?t=1729871824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Like <strong>Mechs</strong>? Like <strong>Deck Builders</strong>? Like <strong>Mech-Deck Builders</strong>!? Choose your MECH, choose your PILOT, and defend your planet from invasion using giant machines of war. Salvage improved weapons and defense systems for your MECH, learn new and improved PILOT skills, and make difficult decisions as you scout the battlefield and repel the invaders! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075760/extras/e6ddd70df27fdd365f66347a2baef807.avif?t=1729871824\" width=334 height=84 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Powerful War Machines</strong>: every mech and pilot is unique, with special quirks and play styles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect Information</strong>: use your knowledge of the battlefield and your opponents capabilities to plan your strategy. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Dynamic Deck Building</strong>: salvage new weapons and armour, upgrade your skills, abilities, and components, build a better mech! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Choose Your Path</strong>: will you engage tougher opponents for greater rewards, will you seek the safer routes?  </p></li></u